Billionaire businessman, Ned Nwoko, has been spotted goofing around with singer, Teni at his home. The politician could be seen in a video teaching the singer how to swim. Videos of their swimming lessons were shared on Instagram by the politician’s wife, Regina Daniels. Recall, Daniels had taken to the photo-sharing platform to celebrate her husband’s 59th birthday in a unique way. The actress made a video which consists of never before seen pictures of them from one of their trips outside Nigeria. Watch video below: Source